snippet.title: Stone Story RPG - Alpha Trailer (2016)
snippet.description:
Release Announcement: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7dUyz29cizI
Stone Story is an RPG set in a dark and ominous world. The unique visual style is achieved through text-based ascii animations. Learn more about this game at StoneStoryRPG.com
